Aşağıdaki payment gateway kodu için comprehensive `pytest` unit testleri yaz. Mock / patch kullanarak harici HTTP çağrılarını izole et. Fixture, parametrized test ve exception case'lerini kapsa. Sadece test kodu:

```python
import requests

class PaymentGateway:
    def __init__(self, api_key: str):
        self.api_key = api_key
        self.base_url = "https://api.payment.com/v1"

    def charge(self, amount: float, card_token: str) -> dict:
        resp = requests.post(
            f"{self.base_url}/charges",
            headers={"Authorization": f"Bearer {self.api_key}"},
            json={"amount": amount, "card_token": card_token}
        )
        resp.raise_for_status()
        return resp.json()

    def refund(self, charge_id: str) -> dict:
        resp = requests.post(
            f"{self.base_url}/charges/{charge_id}/refund",
            headers={"Authorization": f"Bearer {self.api_key}"}
        )
        resp.raise_for_status()
        return resp.json()
```

